(23, 'site.ket_rto', 'Keterangan Ready to Offer', 'Investment opportunities that are ready to be offered to investors, comply with the Medium-Term National/Regional Development Plan, the location offered is suitable to the designation in the Spatial Plan, clear and clean ownership status (not in dispute), and feasible from legal, technical and financial aspects based on Pre-Feasibility Study.', NULL, 'text_area', 18, 'Site'),
