(87, 'proyeks', 'project_name', 3, 'en', 'Solo Convention-Exhibition Hall Development', '2019-09-09 02:01:53', '2019-09-18 01:52:13'),
(88, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 3, 'en', 'Surakarta City is a city that always organizes numerous compelling events every year but unfortunately there is no place that can be used to hold various events at the present. In order to support the Government program in making Surakarta City as the city of MICE (meetings, incentives, conventions, exhibitions), it is necessary to build a convention-exhibition hall which later can become a venue of large amount of local, national, as well as international scale events. The area chosen to build the convention exhibition hall is the area of Surakarta City Warehousing and Various Enterprises (PAU) regional housing in Pendaringan with an area of 27,500 m2 which will be divided into 12,500 m2 for the convention-exhibition hall and 15,000 m2 for parking area. Planned supporting facilities in this convention-exhibition hall consists of meeting rooms, supporting rooms, food court, office and mini store, guest house also parking area.', '2019-09-09 02:05:32', '2019-09-09 02:05:32'),
(89, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 3, 'en', 'Solo Convention Exhibition Hall development with total area of 3.6 hectares which includes a building area of 12,500 m2 with facilities of 4 Convention and exhibition buildings with a capacity of 12,000 people, 6 metting rooms, VIP rooms, parking spaces 15,000m2, food center, jogging tracks, and city parks.', '2019-09-09 02:05:32', '2019-09-09 02:05:32'),
(90, 'proyeks', 'eksisting', 3, 'en', 'Pedaringan Trading and Various Business Regional Public Company of Surakarta City has a sufficient land available for the development of this Convention-Exhibition Hall', '2019-09-09 02:05:32', '2019-09-09 02:05:32'),
