(114, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 6, 'en', 'Shrimp fisheries industry is a fisheries industry that concerns to all process of fisheries products, specifically Whiteleg shrimp, namely from supplying the demand of shrimp feed to processing the result of Whiteleg shrimp farms aimed to foreign market. Activities that will be developed in this integrated shrimp fisheries activities are shrimp feed factory, Whiteleg shrimp seeding, cultivation farm, and Whiteleg shrimp processing factory. The chosen location to be established for this integrated shrimp fisheries industry is Binangun Sub-district. Participation from the local community is expected in order to support the sustainability of the plan to establish an integrated industry of shrimp fisheries. This participation can be given by the community by being a collaborative partner in various businesses supporting the integrated fisheries shrimp industry.', '2019-09-09 02:27:23', '2019-09-09 02:27:23'),
(115, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 6, 'en', 'Development of 4 integrated factories, namely shrimp feed factory, hatchery, cultivation farm, and shrimp processing factory.', '2019-09-09 02:27:23', '2019-09-09 02:27:23'),
(116, 'proyeks', 'eksisting', 6, 'en', 'There is a huge chance to develop Whiteleg Shrimp cultivation with an orientation to be exported in particular and other fisheries industries in Cilacap Regency. It is important to build an integrated industry in Cilacap Regency, specializing in frozen products of fresh Whiteleg Shrimp. This integrated industry concerns all the sectors related, from feed mill, hatchery, enlarging, to processing.', '2019-09-09 02:27:23', '2019-09-09 02:27:23'),
(117, 'proyeks', 'status_kepemilikan', 6, 'en', 'Cilacap Regency Government', '2019-09-09 02:27:23', '2019-09-09 02:27:23'),
