(141, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 75, 'en', 'Greneng Reservoir is located in Tunjungan Village, Tunjungan Sub-district, Blora Regency, which borders Rembang Regency and adjacent to KPH Mantingan Rembang Forest. The presence of Greneng Reservoir is also supported by human resource which has a role to fulfill the needs of tourists. Community around the place utilizes natural resources to be processed as foods, handicrafts, and sellers. This community also provides other services such as transportation, guide, parking service, until outbound. The attraction of Greneng Reservoir is its own scenery as well as the Cemoro Pitu Hill, which has a background of teak and rosewood forests. In addition, there are still many vacant lots that can be developed to improve its charm such as building bird breeding and flower gardens around Greneng Reservoir.', '2019-09-09 02:36:03', '2019-09-09 02:36:03'),
