(149, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 76, 'en', 'Morosari Beach, which is located in Bedono Village, Sayung Sub-District, Demak Regency, has a potential to be one of marine tourism sites in Demak Regency. The availability of extensive land drives the management company to build various facilities which are able to support the existence of Morosari Beach Marine Tourism. As for facilities which will be developed, Morosari Beach offered hostels, restaurants, and fishing spots. There are also water games like waterpark, water spider, lazy river, ocean park, and swimming pool. Asides from water games, this place also provide water sport facilities, such as banana boat and water polo. In addition, this beach will offer in-land rides, such as ferris wheel, ball pool, bumper cars, and outbound. Mangrove flourish around the beach and will be developed to support the beauty of Morosari Beach Marine Tourism.', '2019-09-09 02:39:07', '2019-09-09 02:39:07'),
