(167, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 78, 'en', 'Grobogan Regency Receipt System Development is a legal entity that will execute a series of activities involving recording, storing, transferring ownership, charging mortgaging, reporting, as well as providing systems and information networks for the warehouse receipt registration center. Grobogan Warehouse Receipt System will be utilized for the storage of commodities produced by the farmers, including rice and corn. Besides storing, this warehouse receipt system can also produce good quality rice with the brand “Srikandi Grobogan”. Grobogan Warehouse Receipt System Management is very professional because it also cooperates with farmers, farmer groups, and even Village Owned Enterprises (BUMDes) to become partners through numerous partnership programs, such as rice production facilities, capital loans for farmers, rice farming insurance, and rice procurement partnerships for Noncash Food Aid program (BPNT).', '2019-09-09 02:44:03', '2019-09-09 02:44:03'),
