(230, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 87, 'en', 'The location of Tlogo Wening Agro Educational Park (Tlogo Wening Agro Edu Park) is in Delik Village, Tuntang Sub-district, Semarang Regency and is an integrated tourism area development through the integration of Tlogo, Bawen, and Rawa Pening area. This place is also developed in the creative economic sector as tourism site. Located at an altitude of 430-675 meters above sea level, Tlogo Wening Agro Edu Park has an iconic Rawa Pening Lake which is one of Central Java’s tourism landmarks. Rawa Pening becomes the main attraction because it is the biggest natural lake in Java Island with an area of 2,670 Ha. Besides of Rawa Pening, other attraction of Tlogo Wening Agro Edu Park is the panorama of Merbabu Mount, Telomoyo, and Ungaran. The number of visitors to the park over the past three years shows a significant increase of 37,282 visitors per year, consisting of 36,850 domestic tourists and 532 foreign tourists. This number of visitors increased four times more than in previous years.', '2019-09-09 03:17:37', '2019-09-09 03:17:37'),
(231, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 87, 'en', 'Tlogo Wening Agroedupark Development includes hotels, cottages, transportation, children\'s entertainment, stage performances, campsites, educational facilities, farm-farm-plantation tours, office buildings.', '2019-09-09 03:17:37', '2019-09-09 03:17:37'),
