(248, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 89, 'en', 'Salatiga Souvenir Center is a place that will become the marketing center of various types of Micro, Small, and Medium Enterprises (MSMEs) products from Salatiga and be equipped with other supporting facilities and infrastructure. The chosen location for this souvenir center is Blotongan Sub-district with an area of 5.5 Ha that currently are vacant lands and rice fields. This place needs to be made because of the growth of MSMEs in Salatiga, especially traditional food products because the demand and interest in these products are very high. The presence of the souvenir center on the edge of the Salatiga Ring Road is expected to be able to attract more tourists because of its strategic location and can be visited by large buses. In addition, the average of MSMEs have respective workers so the availability of human resources can be said are very adequate.', '2019-09-09 03:23:30', '2019-09-09 03:23:30'),
