(257, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 90, 'en', 'Semarang City has MICE (meetings, incentives, conferences, exhibitions) events that are organized quite often and sometimes even the tourists come with a purpose to hold these events. As we can see that there is a high interest of MICE activities while the lack of adequate facilities for organizing these activities to the fullest, Semarang City needs spaces, specifically built to accommodate these kinds of event, with variety of proper facilities. It is expected that with these facilities, it can increase the management of major events in Semarang City. By having an architectural style that reflects technological advance, this facility will be named Semarang Expo Center. The Semarang Expo Center is expected to increase Semarang’s economic activities which will also impact to tourism, employment, and education sector.', '2019-09-09 03:35:35', '2019-09-09 03:35:35'),
(258, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 90, 'en', 'The Semarang Expo Center development will include construction on 3 halls, 1 ball room, 4 meeting rooms, 1 lounge, 1 open theater, hotel capacity of 75 rooms, bio filter waste treatment, and expo center with the capacity of 5,000-7,000 people ', '2019-09-09 03:35:35', '2019-09-09 03:35:35'),
