(266, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 91, 'en', 'Industrial sector is the growing sector in Boyolali Regency, especially in urban suburbs area. The development of this industrial sector is able to provide employment opportunities for the community to become labor in factories and workers for regional development projects as well as produce business opportunities for the surrounding community. Plans for industrial allotment areas will be directed to areas that are not in disaster-prone areas, which are Blumbang Village and Jaten Village in Klego Sub-district, Boyolali Regency. This territory is one of the sub-districts in Boyolali Regency which functions as an Environmental Service Center with potential land for industrial area construction with an area of 52.6 Ha. The facilities and infrastructure in Blumbang Village and Jaten Villages are equipped with power grid and telecommunication networks which are the basic needs of industrial and port operators who support the delivery of raw materials that are oriented to regions and abroad.', '2019-09-09 03:38:02', '2019-09-09 03:38:02'),
