(275, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 120, 'en', 'The magnificent view of Kemuning Park makes 1.500 visitors per day come to travel. Activities generally done by tourists are enjoying the cool and view of mountains and tea plantation, strolling around, and enjoying local dishes. With those potentials that its owned, Kemuning Park will develop other facilities and rides in order to increase visitors’ interest to come here. Mostly Kemuning Park tourists come from Surakarta City, Sragen Regency, Sukoharjo Regency, Klaten Regency, Boyolali Regency, Ngawi Regency, Magetan Regency, Ponorogo Regency, and Balinese who performs Hinduism ritual as well as foreign tourists. As for facilities and rides that will be developed in Kemuning Park are glass bridge, Jeep adventure arena, trail adventure arena, golf field, paragliding runaways and landings, outbound, folk culinary store, and other facilities that will make visitors feel at home. ', '2019-09-09 03:45:29', '2019-09-09 03:45:29'),
(276, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 120, 'en', '1.	Glass Bridge  2.	Jeep Adventure Area 3.	Motor Cross/Trail Adventure Area 4.	Golf Course 5.	Viewpoint + O34/Thousand Stairs Tower 6.	Runway and Parachute Landing 7.	Terminal Wisata and Parking Area 8.	Out Bond Adventure Teh Kemuning 9.	Kedai Kuliner Rakyat / UKM 10.	Angkutan Wisata 11.	Hospital ', '2019-09-09 03:45:29', '2019-09-09 03:45:29'),
