(284, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 118, 'en', 'Gondang Reservoir Park is located in Kerjo Sub-district, Karanganyar Regency and has an area of 4.400m2. Being the center of attraction for tourists from Solo and other provinces namely Bali, DIY Yogyakarta, East Java, West Java, and foreign visitors as well, the number of tourists came to this place can be up to 23.000 people each month. The location of Gondang Park Reservoir, which is located on a cool high plateau, is one of the reasons for visitors to take a break from urban activities and enjoy a relaxing holiday here. For further development, Gondang Reservoir Park will be added with water recreation, fruit picking agro tourism, outbound, jeep adventure area, art and culture performance area, and other facilities that can support this tourism spot ', '2019-09-09 03:50:49', '2019-09-09 03:50:49'),
