(311, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 94, 'en', 'Rowo Jombor is a nature tourism area where its water area is utilized for floating shops that serve variety of freshwater fish dishes as well as utilized as cages. Its location is in Krakitan Village, Bayat Sub-district, Klaten Regency and has an area of ±198 ha. In its further development, it is planned to build sport center facilities, such as horse racing arena, motorcycle racing arena, and tennis court. In addition, there will also be the construction of a playground, water tourism, and a tower which will be a symbol of Rowo Jombor.', '2019-09-09 04:06:27', '2019-09-09 04:06:27'),
