(329, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 95, 'en', 'Hotels have a role in supporting tourism because they can be used as accommodation option for tourists to stay overnight. The suitable location for the construction of this 3-star hotel is Transmigration Transit of Magelang Regency, which is located on Sunan Giri Street, South Jurangombo Urban Sub-district, South Magelang Sub-district, Magelang City. This location is quite strategic because it is in the middle of the city and in the heart of business center, Indonesian National Army Education Center (AKMIL), as well as the economic center and also surrounded by various tourist destinations. The facilities that will be created in this hotel consist of lobby and accessories with Magelang ethnic designs, 50 units of standard type room, 15 units of suite type room, ensuite bathrooms, meeting rooms, party/event room, restaurant, valet parking, recreational area, swimming pool, spa, and gym. The activities in this hotel will get excellent support from human resources in Magelang Regency of the numerous graduates from vocational schools with several majors, such as hospitality, culinary, office studies, and so on. ', '2019-09-09 04:30:13', '2019-09-09 04:30:13'),
(330, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 95, 'en', 'Building family hotel concept that includes:  -	The hotel concept will be built in the form of a 3-story bulding with ethnic design (Magelang style)  -	Standard room type (50 units with an area of @ 24 m2)  -	Suite room type (15 units with an area of @ 48 m2) -	Meeting room, party/event room (hall) -	In-room bathroom  -	Restaurant that will serve breakfast, lunch, and dinner (Indonesian and international cuisine)  -	Valet parking  -	Recreational park, swimming pool, spa, gym', '2019-09-09 04:30:13', '2019-09-09 04:30:13'),
