(338, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 99, 'en', 'Kartika Swimming Pool, which is located on Veteran Street, Kroyo Village, Karangmalang Sub-district, Sragen Regency, is the main tourist attraction in Sragen Regency because of its strategic location in the central of the city, accessible transportation, and the available facilities. This swimming pool that has an area of ±5,839 m2 is always crowded with visitors from all ages, ranging from children, teens to adults. The further development of Kartika Swimming Pool will transform swimming pool rides into waterpark in the hope that it can increase the growth of small and medium enterprises so as to boost economic growth, especially for the surrounding community. Facilities that will be added in Kartika Swimming Pool are the entrance gate that will be made as a palace entrance, a large parking lot, ticket counters, dressing rooms, bathrooms and urinals, minimarket, and also souvenir kiosk.', '2019-09-09 04:44:46', '2019-09-09 04:44:46'),
