(347, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 100, 'en', 'Kenep Urban Sub-district, Sukoharjo Sub-district, Sukoharjo Regency is one of the areas that will be developed as Kenep Creative Tourist Area. There are six tourism potentials that are owned by Kenep Urban Sub-district, namely Bengawan Solo, Mati River, heritage tourism, industrial education tour, agrotourism and culinary tour, and handicraft. This urban sub-district is developed as a creative tourist village in order to develop the villages and increase the welfare and income of the local community so that it can also change people’s behavior to be cleaner, healthier, orderly, friendly, culture, and religious. The development of Kenep Creative Tourist Village is expected to increase the interest of visitors, starting from education sector in every level to domestic and international tourists.', '2019-09-09 04:48:35', '2019-09-09 04:48:35'),
