(356, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 101, 'en', 'Conto Tourist Village is located in Bulukerto Sub-district, Wonogiri Regency or specifically on the south side of Lawu Mountain hillside. The environment condition of Conto Village consists of hills that are a little steep and steep hills. Generally this area is utilized as plantation area, agriculture area, annual perennials, moor, and residential area. At the present Soko Langit Hermitage has been built as the center destination of Conto Tourist Village. Aside from that, there are also other facilities, such as viewing post, flying fox, gazebo, swimming pool that are still under construction, fruit garden, and vetiver garden.', '2019-09-09 04:53:30', '2019-09-09 04:53:30'),
