(364, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 102, 'en', 'Magelang City has an abandoned asset that is located adequately strategic because it is in the center of the city, specifically at A. Yani Street No. 6, Panjang Urban Sub-district, North Magelang Sub-district. This area of is ± 4.750 m2 used to be a cinema but nowadays there will be a construction in this location, namely utilized to be mall, theater, hotel, and condotel. Its location in the city center and at the main road makes it accessible because of the large number of transportations that pass through the route and the high level of crowds. This is one of the efforts to utilize the abandoned asset appropriately. It is expected that later the development of this region can provide potential for various types of property products around.', '2019-09-09 04:58:02', '2019-09-09 04:58:02'),
