(373, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 103, 'en', 'Merdada Lake is located in the Dieng Plateau, precisely in Karang Tengah Village, Batur Sub-district with the distance of ±55 km from the central government of Banjarnegara Regency. Nowadays this tourist destination is open for visitors however the facilities provided are insufficient. There are three attractions made in the Merdada Lake development concept, namely skywalk area, adventure tourism, and ecotourism. The number of tourist visits to Dieng Plateau in 2017 reached 1,584,477 and this number represented a 100% enhancement compared to the visits in 2012. This can be a remarkable opportunity if Merdada Lake develop an aquatic tourism that combines entertainment tourism, adventure tourism, educational tourism, and cultural tourism. It will be a suitable choice to have a leisure for both domestic visitors, from families to couples, and international tourists.', '2019-09-09 06:41:02', '2019-09-09 06:41:02'),
(374, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 103, 'en', 'The Merdada Lake Tourism Development includes the construction of skywalk rides (glass bridge crossings and photo spots, gazebo views, calla lily flower gardens, and glass water restaurants), adventure tourism (horse riding, kayaking lakes, biking, cottages, hiking and camping), and ecoturism (bird watching (grouse), farming areas (carica and wasabi) and fishing in the lake).', '2019-09-09 06:41:02', '2019-09-09 06:41:02'),
(375, 'proyeks', 'eksisting', 103, 'en', 'Currently it can be enjoyed by tourists but is still limited to the main attraction, such as the lake and its natural scenery', '2019-09-09 06:41:02', '2019-09-09 06:41:02'),
