(382, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 104, 'en', 'Banyumas Regency Government has plans to construct a tower that will be built in Kota Baru area, specifically in Kalibagor Sub-district and Patikraja Sub-district. Kota Baru will have an area of ±600 Ha and envisioned to be a green open space in Banyumas Regency. The future tower in Kota Baru will have a height of 200 m with an area of 2.25 Ha, including basements. This tower will consist of 50 floors, with five basement floors and 45 floors which are proposed to be telecommunication tower, business meeting rooms, Javanese history museum, display area, viewing tower of Purwokerto, and cultural performance venue. Moreover this tower is planned to be the city branding of Banyumas Regency that has some roles as Banyumas icon, Kota Baru development, and also a space for recreational, tourism, cultural, entertainment, science and technology, and educational purposes, as well as trading and event area for various stakeholders.', '2019-09-09 06:42:47', '2019-09-09 06:42:47'),
