(409, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 107, 'en', 'Karangpucung Goat Integrated Area is an effort to develop a goat farm which has only been focused on fattening cultivation for the meat. Furthermore, there will be added a post-harvest handling phase in order to establish a goat milk processing industry. Goat milk is not as popular as cow milk but its presence has its own highly potential market to be further developed. The future goat integrated area will add more productive activities, such as cultivation processing (brood and enlargement), feed supply, and milk processing for consumption. Karangpucung Goat has been chosen for the development because in this location, there is one type of goats that can produce high-quality milk if it is crossed with the Saanen Goat or known as Sapera Goat.', '2019-09-09 07:14:10', '2019-09-09 07:14:10'),
(410, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 107, 'en', 'Construction of two integrated factories, which are the dairy goat cultivation area and goat milk processing factory', '2019-09-09 07:14:10', '2019-09-09 07:14:10'),
(411, 'proyeks', 'eksisting', 107, 'en', 'Maintenance from local community currently still use traditional system. Focus of the maintenance will be directed to enlargement cultivation for the meat. Goat breeding business that have only focused on meat production, will be more profitable if developed towards milk production. Therefore, it is necessary to develop an integrated Karangpucung Goat area that integrates all economic activities, from feed supplying, cultivation area, to processing goat milk in packaging. It is because Karangpucung Goat species itself has a potential for milking ', '2019-09-09 07:14:10', '2019-09-09 07:14:10'),
