(418, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 108, 'en', 'Pekalongan Regency Former Pavilion is located in Pekalongan Regency area, specifically at Nusantara Street No. 1. It becomes a potential location for hotel establishment because the surrounding environment has been formed as a crowd center in Pekalongan area. The surroundings also have high accessibility and near vital objects of the region, namely Pekalongan Regency Square, Kauman Great Mosque of Pekalongan, Matahari Department Store, hotel and ±2 km from Sentono Batik Wholesale Market. In addition, the asset location is only ±2 km from Pekalongan City Train Station and ±4km from Pekalongan City Bus Terminal. ', '2019-09-09 07:23:47', '2019-09-09 07:33:46'),
(419, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 108, 'en', 'Consist of 3 blocks, which are hotel; cultural center, exhibition and convention center; office and shopping arcade. 3-star hotel with 50 rooms (10 suite rooms with an area of 48 m2 and 40 deluxe rooms with an area of 24 m2) equipped with meeting room, function room, board room, lounge lobby, and restaurant. Cultural center, exhibition and convention center consists of functional hall (1,000 seats); art studio (100 seats); and 4 units of exhibition venue. Office and shopping arcade consists of 10 units of office, restaurant with a capacity of 200 seats, 10 units of booth, and a garden arcade.', '2019-09-09 07:23:47', '2019-09-09 07:23:47'),
