(436, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 110, 'en', 'Bumi Shambara offers natural, history, and cultural tourism in one place and is planned to be the Entrance of Purbalingga. This tourist attraction is expected to increase immense attraction tourists from Australia, USA, Canada, and Western Europe to visit Purbalingga. Bumi Shambara Development is designed to protect and support the function of protection forests with the result that can be able to provide economic benefits for the local community. Numerous promising sectors to be developed here are art performance, souvenir shops, culinary spots, and homestays. The potential elements of Bumi Shambara for further development include its physical situation and condition, local wisdom and heritage, traditional culture of the society, flora and fauna, the charm of its panorama, and strategic position. The development is divided into three zones, such as parking lot, Bumi Shambara courtyard, Purba Market and Batu Museum, Cultural Stage, Purba Resort, Purba Park, and agrotourism area of Purbalingga coffee.', '2019-09-09 07:35:54', '2019-09-09 07:35:54'),
(437, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 110, 'en', 'The Bumi Shambara Development includes infrastructure development, construction of primordial-themed market and stone museum, construction of cultural stages, construction of primordial-themed resorts, and construction of primordial-themed parks.', '2019-09-09 07:35:54', '2019-09-09 07:35:54'),
(438, 'proyeks', 'eksisting', 110, 'en', 'The road condition to curug sewu attraction is in perfect condition there are various facilities around curug sewu valthough several privately run hotels are available, the facilities are still lacking telecommunication networks, water resources, public transportation and electricity are available and sufficient there are 8 locations to be developed into 16 zones', '2019-09-09 07:35:54', '2019-09-09 07:35:54'),
