(472, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 114, 'en', 'Tegal Yekan Park is located at Kolonel Sugiono Street No. 152, West Tegal Sub-district, Tegal City. It is developed with the aim to promote tourism in the unity of art, culture, excellence regional products, and culinary and is in accordance with the spirit of Tegal City Government to preserve local culture. This park is provided with promotion and business information center, Tegal Cultural Park and cultural tourism, culinary, as well as excellence regional products. The current condition of Promotion and Business Information Center consists of a hall and 48 stalls that has been utilized for various community events and activities. It is managed by Office of Cooperation, Small Micro Medium Enterprises, and Trading (Dinkop UMKM dan Perdagangan). The future plan of Tegal Yekan Park will be completing some facilities, such as stalls, new toilets, prayer rooms, parking lot for cars and motorcycles, gazebo, gate, name plate, and also guardhouse.', '2019-09-09 07:50:56', '2019-09-09 07:50:56'),
(473, 'proyeks', 'lingkup_pekerjaan', 114, 'en', 'Waterleiding Culinary Park development including the construction of street vendors, Tower of View, coffee shop, museums, restaurants, renovation of dina\'s building.', '2019-09-09 07:50:56', '2019-09-09 07:50:56'),
