(1024, 'proyeks', 'latar_belakang', 132, 'en', 'Rembang Regency is a fairly large sugar cane producing area in Central Java with an area of 6,852 ha for sugarcane plantation. At present, this regency already has a sugar factory but not all sugarcane can be collected. The yield of 4,352 ha of sugarcane plantations cannot yet be accommodated in the sugar factory owned by Rembang Regency. This condition can be a potential to develop a new sugar factory in order to accommodate more sugarcane plantations. This sugar factory development will be located in Pasarbanggi Village, Rembang Regency. Aside from accommodating,, this plan can also increase income and welfare of sugarcane farmers as well to provide employment opportunities for the surrounding community.', '2019-09-19 02:53:33', '2019-09-19 02:53:33');
